55:09.120 --> 55:12.248
Well, you're not normal.

55:12.415 --> 55:13.916
Most of us aren't.

55:14.084 --> 55:17.753
Okay, not everything is connected
to being an alcoholic.

55:19.589 --> 55:22.341
I'm not just talking about alcoholics.

55:22.509 --> 55:24.677
People are fucking weird.

55:25.011 --> 55:29.014
We all have shit that we carry in our
heads that doesn't make any sense.

55:29.641 --> 55:32.685
At least alcoholics have the tools
to work through it.

55:32.852 --> 55:37.064
Steps.

55:37.232 --> 55:39.316
And talking...

55:40.193 --> 55:43.445
...listening, crying.

55:43.613 --> 55:46.240
Yeah, I have the crying part
all worked out.

55:46.408 --> 55:48.617
I know, right?

55:50.328 --> 55:52.705
I think my first year...

55:52.872 --> 55:57.376
