for you.

56:44.758 --> 56:46.425
Oh, my God, I feel awful.

56:46.593 --> 56:49.345
I know this is a hard time,
you have to keep going.

56:49.512 --> 56:50.679
You have to be strong.

56:50.847 --> 56:53.098
I feel so awful.
I can't keep doing this.

56:53.266 --> 56:56.685
If you wanna take a day off,
maybe through the weekend.

56:56.853 --> 56:58.729
No, I need to be honest with you.

57:01.274 --> 57:02.775
Okay.

57:08.490 --> 57:10.657
Principal Barnes...

57:13.286 --> 57:14.912
...I was never pregnant.

57:18.375 --> 57:20.793
But you vomited in class.

57:21.169 --> 57:23.921
